{{notability|Organizations|date=January 2014}} The '''Royal Society of Fine Arts (RSFA)''' is a non-governmental, non-profit cultural organization, founded in [[Amman]], Jordan in 1979.<ref>http://universes-in-universe.org/eng/nafas/articles/2003/jngfa_royal_soc_of_fine_arts</ref> Its goal is to encourage cultural diversity, disseminate artistic knowledge and promote art from the Islamic and [[developing countries]].
